        "value": "{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}i^{0}&=1,&i^{1}&=i,&i^{2}&=-1,&i^{3}&=-i,\\\\i^{4}&=1,&i^{5}&=i,&i^{6}&=-1,&i^{7}&=-i\\\\&\\vdots &&\\vdots &&\\vdots &&\\vdots \\end{aligned}}}"
